SUMMARY:Rising Explorers - Summer Youth Internship Program Info Session
LOCATION:2555 E Hanna Ave Tampa \, FL 33610 United States
DESCRIPTION:Come learn more about this years Rising Explorer - Summer Yout
 h Internship Program for HCPS students ages 16-19 The Summer Youth Intern-
 Rising Explorers will Explore and learn about a variety of entry-level car
 eers within various departments in the City of Tampa Learn about the core 
