 h of Sade\, this gathering is an invitation to slow down\, connect\, and a
 rrive fully--in your body\, in your truth\, and in community This is a spa
 ce for conversation\, music\, reflection\, and warmth. A reminder that lov
 e\, tenderness\, and intimacy are radical acts--especially in a world that
  rushes us past them. Come as you are. Arrive open. Let the weekend unfold
 . Limited capacity \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/186556
