SUMMARY:Tampa Fire Rescue Annual Open House
LOCATION:808 E. Zack St Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a fun\, family-friendly day with TampasBravest at 
 our Annual Open House in downtown Tampa!  Saturday\, April 11\, 2026  10 a
 .m.  2 p.m.  Station 1 (808 E. Zack St.) Tampa Firefighters Museum (720 E.
  Zack St.) Come meet your firefighters\, check out our trucks and equipmen
 t\, watch live demonstrations\, and enjoy hands-on activities for kids and
  adults alike. This is a great chance to learn more about what we do and h
 ow we serve the Tampa community every day. Free and open to the public. Br
